<paragraph id="1BB92177AB9351CA24B11BE4C73D3CC4" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1D43497BE678DBE1BD4371F4A021C47D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">China (Shaanxi).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="A2D8A44C6DCBB36F95AC402A5CD7346F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="102DDF9D8E93777F03CABF3C46021C2A" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="94586B3C072AA26F3B4259CBA3DE176D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
This species is named in honour of Mrs Ma Yun, who collected many materials of 
<taxonomicName id="80060713137B67C3A07491F602B26B2A" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Agriotypus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Agriotypus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="39A795338BAF89C650F13E1781E2BC7F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Agriotypus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and provided a lot of help in our research work.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
